17:32.631 --> 17:35.464
and, um, a gentleman.

17:36.464 --> 17:38.130
My last name was Italian,

17:38.214 --> 17:40.881
so he seemed
to take a liking to me.

17:40.964 --> 17:42.881
First thing he said
to me, he was like,

17:42.964 --> 17:44.464
"Hey, here's some
money, go eat, go eat."

17:44.547 --> 17:46.422
And I just thought
