17:46.506 --> 17:47.923
that's how Italians are.

17:48.005 --> 17:49.506
And it just made me feel

17:49.589 --> 17:52.464
at ease with him,
that this is a good person.

17:54.839 --> 17:57.214
I never knew he was married.
