18:22.631 --> 18:24.839
And I was like, "Wow,
so many people are trying

18:24.923 --> 18:26.923
"to win this thing,
and you're sitting here

18:27.005 --> 18:28.547
with all four pieces."
[laughs]

18:28.631 --> 18:30.589
You know, I'm like, "What?"

18:30.673 --> 18:31.839
"If you're interested,"
he says,

18:31.923 --> 18:33.923
"just walk in McDonald's

18:34.005 --> 18:35.923
"and this is what you gotta do

18:36.005 --> 18:38.422
and this is how it rolls."

18:38.506 --> 18:40.381
He goes,
"I'll give you 20,000 now

18:40.464 --> 18:43.255
and I'll give you
another 10,000 later."

18:43.339 --> 18:45.214
And I thought,
"Wow, that's a lot of money,"

18:45.297 --> 18:47.089
You know what I mean?
I could go buy me a car,

18:47.172 --> 18:49.255
you know, I could go do
some stuff, you know...

18:49.339 --> 18:51.756
'cause back then, you know,
I'm working at the airlines,

18:51.839 --> 18:55.297
what am I making?
