18:55.381 --> 18:58.339
I was game for
something exhilarating.

19:01.172 --> 19:03.005
So he had me fly to Philly.

19:03.089 --> 19:05.589
Being with I'm with
the airlines, I can do that.

19:05.673 --> 19:07.798
He picked me up
at the airport,

19:07.881 --> 19:09.714
we drove right to McDonald's

19:09.798 --> 19:12.089
and I didn't even have
