19:21.673 --> 19:23.547
And he's like,
"Huh.

19:23.631 --> 19:25.381
So you're the winner."

19:26.255 --> 19:28.547
It was just too easy.

19:31.881 --> 19:33.631
But I didn't know...

19:33.714 --> 19:36.506
the aftermath
that was to follow.

19:36.589 --> 19:39.005
I mean, 'cause there was things
that nobody knew,

19:39.089 --> 19:42.589
and I just
kept it all to myself.

19:49.089 --> 19:51.506
- My husband,
he picked the winners,

19:51.589 --> 19:53.589
but he kept picking Italians

19:53.673 --> 19:56.339
on the East Coast.

19:56.422 --> 19:59.589
They were--they were kind of
being stupid about it.

20:00.756 --> 20:03.506
Somebody was bound
to get suspicious,

20:03.589 --> 20:05.339
so I told my husband,

20:05.422 --> 20:07.881
"I've got a friend
