27:43.047 --> 27:44.964
- Before my husband
was working

27:45.047 --> 27:47.130
the Monopoly fraud game,

27:47.214 --> 27:51.464
we had my son,
Francesco Gennaro Colombo.

27:51.547 --> 27:55.089
[indistinct speech]

27:55.172 --> 27:57.130
- Say hi to the camera,
Frankie.

27:57.214 --> 28:00.005
- Hi, camera!
