Easy.

28:04.881 --> 28:07.089
- Basketball.

28:07.172 --> 28:08.506
- [laughing]

28:08.589 --> 28:11.339
- I was, at times,
really very happy.

28:11.422 --> 28:14.547
I had my son.
I had some money.

28:14.631 --> 28:17.964
I should've at least
been having a good time.

28:19.506 --> 28:22.005
But I was never satisfied,
ever.

28:22.089 --> 28:24.172
Um, I went from home to home

28:24.255 --> 28:26.047
thinking that one
was gonna make it better.

28:26.130 --> 28:27.589
You don't have friends.

28:27.673 --> 28:30.422
You can't bring friends
into that lifestyle.

28:32.381 --> 28:35.172
Even though
I adored my husband,

28:35.255 --> 28:37.714
I found out he had
a mistress on the side,

28:37.798 --> 28:39.923
which I guess is a prerequisite

28:40.005 --> 28:43.464
of an Italian gangster
to have a mistress.

28:50.631 --> 28:53.255
I was walking down the hallway
to check on Frankie,

28:53.339 --> 28:55.798
while he was sleeping,
when I heard my husband

28:55.881 --> 29:00.172
on the telephone saying, um...

29:00.255 --> 29:04.047
some unsavory words to her.

29:04.130 --> 29:06.381
And I barged in and I said,

29:06.464 --> 29:08.130
"Who the hell
are you talking to?"

29:08.214 --> 29:10.964
And I took the phone
from him.

29:12.172 --> 29:15.506
And I took it, and I
slammed it across his face.

29:15.589 --> 29:17.255
- They did get
in a lot of fights.

29:17.339 --> 29:20.339
Um, she would say a lot
of mean, nasty things to him.

29:20.422 --> 29:22.589
She was very abusive,
as far as physical--

29:22.673 --> 29:24.255
slapping
and so forth and so on.

29:24.339 --> 29:27.589
Robin would just try
swinging and clawing at him.

29:27.673 --> 29:30.589
I mean, he would grab her hands
and say, "Stop, stop, stop it."

29:30.673 --> 29:33.381
[doorbell rings]

29:36.172 --> 29:38.464
- Anytime I threatened
to leave him,

29:38.547 --> 29:41.172
Uncle Jerry would step in.

29:43.839 --> 29:47.589
Send 15 grand, buy me a car,

29:47.673 --> 29:50.297
