29:50.381 --> 29:52.506
And, um...

29:54.339 --> 29:56.506
So I wouldn't leave.

29:58.339 --> 30:01.923
- My brother was always making
money and he was never home.

30:02.005 --> 30:04.089
He always had
an excuse to go somewhere,

30:04.172 --> 30:06.089
to go on a business trip,
to be somewhere.

30:06.172 --> 30:09.047
Um...so I knew he wasn't happy.

