He wanted to do
classy places.

30:54.422 --> 30:55.714
- He had his morals.

30:55.798 --> 30:57.214
- Yeah, he had--
he had his morals.

30:57.297 --> 30:58.881
- I got girls
in Daisy Dukes, tops.

30:58.964 --> 31:02.130
I got volleyball courts
being built outside, um...

31:02.214 --> 31:04.464
I have live concerts
here on the weekends.

31:04.547 --> 31:06.172
Basically,
that's about it, really.

31:06.255 --> 31:08.130
- He wanted to make,
like, a gentlemen's club.

31:08.214 --> 31:10.381
And his goal was to open up
four or five of these

31:10.464 --> 31:13.089
all through Hilton Head
and North and South Carolina.

31:13.172 --> 31:14.673
The county
kept on fighting him

31:14.756 --> 31:17.172
and fighting him
and fighting him.

31:17.255 --> 31:19.839
They kept on shutting him down
for this permit, that permit.

31:19.923 --> 31:21.422
- That's not gonna
stop you from...

