- That's not gonna stop us.
My attorney told me

31:23.547 --> 31:26.255
we can--I mean, whatever
we gotta do, we're gonna do.

31:26.339 --> 31:28.297
I mean, I'm out here trying
to earn a living for my family

31:28.381 --> 31:29.714
just like you are,
and that's it.

31:29.798 --> 31:31.047
- I was proud of him

31:31.130 --> 31:32.589
for actually doing
something legal for once.

31:32.673 --> 31:33.881
- The one time he tried
to do something legit.

31:33.964 --> 31:35.339
- Right?

31:35.422 --> 31:36.673
- Some people have
already trickled in

31:36.756 --> 31:37.881
to the establishment here...

31:37.964 --> 31:40.798
- Coming soon, Fuzzy Bunny's.

31:40.881 --> 31:42.631
I hate it so much.

31:42.714 --> 31:45.714
And I told my husband,
I said, "I know you,

31:45.798 --> 31:48.214
"you couldn't just
open a club.

31:48.297 --> 31:51.005
You have to try 'em out."

31:51.089 --> 31:53.964
And I told him to stop.

31:54.047 --> 31:55.381
- There is an existing
court order

31:55.464 --> 31:57.506
where the club
cannot be opened.

31:59.714 --> 32:02.339
- Three months later,
I thought he had sold it

32:02.422 --> 32:05.881
or whatever,
so no more Fuzzy Bunny.

32:05.964 --> 32:10.005
And then one night my son and I
went out to dinner,

32:10.089 --> 32:13.255
and he was like two,
about two years old.

32:13.339 --> 32:16.547
We're driving down the road,
and I pass Fuzzy Bunny.

32:16.631 --> 32:18.756
And I looked,
and there's a bunch of guys

32:18.839 --> 32:21.089
and I'm like,
