32:21.172 --> 32:23.005
I got a little closer,
and I said,

32:23.089 --> 32:24.673
"And there's my
big, fat husband."

32:24.756 --> 32:30.130
And I turned around and I
jumped up on the curb and I--

32:32.589 --> 32:34.422
And Jerry,
he was sitting back

32:34.506 --> 32:38.047
like a big,
fat cat on the phone.

32:38.130 --> 32:40.589
And I just punched him
right in the jaw.

32:40.673 --> 32:43.547
I said, "You are so divorced."

